highlights.text: Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “You’re Losing Me (From The Vault)” is the highest at #7.
“This Christmas” by Donny Hathaway is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 56 spots at #98.
“MY HOUSE” by Beyoncé is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #56.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 185 weeks straight.
